Building on Linux
-----------------

Requirements:
mono-xbuild libsdl-gfx1.2-4 libsdl-mixer1.2 libsdl-ttf2.0-0 libgdiplus

1. Run `./build.sh -r Sprung.sln`
2. That's it! The built game is in ./bin/Release
4. See ./src/installer/debian/PACKAGING for info about creating a Debian package

Building on Windows
-------------------

1. Open 'Sprung.sln' with Microsoft Visual C# 2008 Express Edition
2. Build the project (shortcut key is F6)
3. That's it! The built game is in ./bin/Release
4. See ./src/installer/windows/PACKAGING for info about creating an installer

